    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<pre><code>List myArrayList  = Collections.synchronizedList(new ArrayList());\n\n//add your elements  \n myArrayList.add();\n myArrayList.add();\n myArrayList.add();\n\nsynchronized(myArrayList) {\n    Iterator i = myArrayList.iterator(); \n     while (i.hasNext()){\n         Object  object = i.next();\n     }\n }\n</code></pre>\n"
