    "body" : "<p>Java 8 user can do that: <code>list.removeIf(...)</code></p>\n\n<pre><code>    List&lt;String&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;(Arrays.asList(\"a\", \"b\", \"c\"));\n    list.removeIf(e -&gt; (someCondition));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>It will remove elements in the list, for which someCondition is satisfied</p>\n"
